+
+# Cavecrew
+
+Use when user explicitly allows subagents or asks for delegation plus compact
+agent output.
+
+## Presets
+
+- Investigator: path:line evidence, key finding, unknowns.
+- Builder: changed files, scope, verification, blockers.
+- Reviewer: findings first, severity, file:line, test gaps.
+
+Keep output terse. No long prose.
